were wounded in the battle of the bulge you sort of look at that as that was one compartment of your life this is another compartment of your life it's nothing that you really dwelled on is that right

26:20.543 --> 26:23.227
[Spec Gammon]: Yeah, I didn't dwell on that after I got out of it.

26:24.208 --> 26:25.049
[Spec Gammon]: Tried to forget it.

26:26.972 --> 26:28.834
[Tom Turbiville]: But it was still a proud time of your life, right?

26:28.854 --> 26:30.717
[Tom Turbiville]: I mean, proud to serve.

26:30.737 --> 26:34.242
[Spec Gammon]: Oh, yes, yes.

26:35.724 --> 26:41.952
[Tom Turbiville]: Before we have a chance to go, right now you're working through an injury, but you're about to be back on the golf course again.

26:42.012 --> 26:42.473
[Tom Turbiville]: Is that right?

26:42.673 --> 26:45.317
[Spec Gammon]: Yeah, I got a little pulled hamstring.

26:45.337 --> 26:45.437
[Spec Gammon]: Yeah.

26:46.193 --> 26:47.316
[Spec Gammon]: I'll be back for long.

26:47.576 --> 26:48.278
[Tom Turbiville]: Indeed.

26:48.298 --> 26:51.927
[Tom Turbiville]: Spec is one of the fine senior golfers around this.

26:52.007 --> 27:00.507
[Tom Turbiville]: As a matter of fact, you might not remember this, but I was actually playing with you on the back nine at Bryan Municipal Golf Course the day that you shot a 63.

27:01.567 --> 27:03.611
[Tom Turbiville]: I played with you those last nine holes.

27:03.631 --> 27:08.419
[Tom Turbiville]: I don't know if you remember that or not, but you remember shooting that 63 at Bryan Municipal Golf Course, don't you?

27:08.439 --> 27:13.308
[Spec Gammon]: And I had a 62 and a 63 there within about a two-week period.

27:13.328 --> 27:13.729
[Tom Turbiville]: Indeed.

27:13.929 --> 27:15.111
[Spec Gammon]: No longer, though.

27:15.452 --> 27:16.994
[Tom Turbiville]: And he's still pretty strong about that.

27:17.215 --> 27:17.676
[Tom Turbiville]: Absolutely.

27:17.916 --> 27:20.260
[Tom Turbiville]: Spec Gammon, thank you for being with us today.

27:20.280 --> 27:21.743
[Spec Gammon]: Well, thank you, Tom, for having me.

27:21.943 --> 27:22.444
[Tom Turbiville]: Thank you.

